183CFC31.Line7.10088C: On to business, then: I shall tell Orton to meet me in the storage cellar in Backwater. Give us the privacy to sort this whole thing out.

687327FE.VoiceDir7.10088C: Serious, slightly bitter. No joking here. Lyndon is in all business mode.

8EB1FEEB.Line1.10088C: So, not a waste of time after all.

F0C0A5F3.Line9.10088C: I’d like you there when that happens. I’m not much for gambling anymore.
